SAUCE INGREDIENTS: HOT SAUCE (AGED CAYENNE PEPPERS, DISTILLED VINEGAR, SALT), CORN SYRUP, SOYBEAN OIL, WATER, CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF THE FOLLOWING: DISTILLED VINEGAR, MODIFIED CORN STARCH, MALTODEXTRIN, XANTHAN GUM, PAPRIKA, GARLIC POWDER, SALT, EXTRACTIVES OF PAPRIKA, SPICES, MODIFIED BUTTER OIL, BUTTER FLAVOR, CITRIC ACID, DEHYDRATED BUTTER, SHORTENING POWDER, GUAR GUM, SODIUM BICARBONATE, ANNATTO AND TURMERIC (FOR COLOR), TOCOPHEROL (VITAMIN E).
